=== recommended_attack_surface_reduction_(ASR)_for_devices ===

intune.microsoft.com - Microsoft Intune Admin Center

Devices > Enroll devices > Windows enrollment > MDM/MAM user scope - Change setting to All for both.

Endpoint Security > Attack Surface Reduction Rules > Create Policy > Select Platform (Windows 10, Windows 11, and Windows Server) > Select profile > Attack Surface Reduction Rules > Call policy `asrTest`

the asr policy will get deployed onto device soonafter

--- To speed this up and trigger sync ---
Settings > Accounts > Access work or school > Connected by <Account>
Sync and/or reboot

--- To see if the ASR rule deployed ---
intune.microsoft.com > Endpoint security > Attack surface reduction > Select <Your asr policy>, review status
